FATEs_Escort_Color My World_Desc: The Songbirds have taken the stage! Speak with the royal handmaiden to get dressed and join the show!
FATEs_Escort_Main Street Spectral Parade: The Continental Circus wants you for its splendidly spooky parade. While transfigured, follow the ogre pumpkinhead along Emerald Avenue and cast the Festal Cant charm on the citizens who have come to spectate.
FATEs_Kill Boss_Counter-fiend Training:: A malodorous morbol is wreaking havoc most foul in the city. Strike down the creature known as Cirrate Christelle and rid Ul'dah of its rancid existence.
FATEs_Kill Boss_Counter-void Training: A: A hulking voidsent has forced its way into the city. Strike down the creature known as Benandonner and return it to the aether whence it came.
FATEs_Kill Boss_Counter-void Training: B: An enormous voidsent has forced its way into the city. Strike down this gargoyle known as Baraqiel and return it to the aether whence it came.
FATEs_Slay enemies_Counter-imperial Trai: Imperial assault troops have breached the city walls. Engage the enemy and strike them down to the last man and machina.

FATEs_Slay enemies_Counter-void Training: Fearsome fiends and voidsent have forced their way into the city. Strike down these creatures and rid Ul'dah of their existence.

Instancecontenttextdata_38905_Text: No more tricks, Bakool Ja Ja! We're settling this here and now!
Instancecontenttextdata_38906_Text: Still playing the part of the brave warrior.
Instancecontenttextdata_38909_Text: My magic should be more than enough for Miss Mittens!
Instancecontenttextdata_38912_Text: It's time we finished her, Brother.
Instancecontenttextdata_38913_Text: This is the end for you, kitten!
Instancecontenttextdata_38917_Text: Miss Mittens...is no longer amusing me, Brother!
